TITLE: Registering Components and Systems in EliCS World in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates registering custom components and systems with the World instance to define ECS behavior. Dependencies include user-defined PositionComponent and MovementSystem, and registration order is important: components should be registered before systems to satisfy system query dependencies.
